ta-lib (finance libraries)

TA-Lib provides common functions for the technical analysis of financial market data.

Widely used by trading software developers working with Excel, .NET, Java, Perl, Python or C/C++.
 
* bullet More than 150 technical analysis indicators such as ADX, MACD, RSI, Stochastic, Bollinger Bands etc...
* bullet Includes candlestick pattern recognition.
* bullet Optional abstract API allowing your code to adapt automatically when new functions are added!

 BSD License: Can be used freely in open-source or commercial software

http://ta-lib.org/
